citrix Xenserver files
----------------------

These steps must be done one every new xenserver

* The scripts must be copied to /usr/local/bin
* The package sudo must be installed on the xenserver
* lines of sudoers must be added to /etc/sudoers
* a user named citrix_info must be created
* the file authorized_keys must be copied to ~citrix_info/.ssh 
  chown citrix_info -R ~citrix_info
  chmod go-rwx -R ~citrix_info/.ssh
  
